originalText.text:
Hello,
I had a great experience at my follow up appointment with Anna Larkin. She is a very sharp and professional Nurse Practitioner listening carefully, analyzing and answering all my questions.
I was very please with the overall experience.
I am now waiting for my next appointment with Dr Neel Metha knowing that Anna has understood my needs and established a list of actions to submit to Dr Metha.
I left Weill Cornell knowing I was on the right pass to recovery.
Thanks for everything.
Best
Karine Jones

originalText.text: Outstanding professional. Asked excellent questions and actually listened—not all professionals are good at listening to patients. There were questions that needed to be referred to the physician and Anna followed up promptly even though it  was after office hours.

originalText.text: Anna Larkin N.P is a great Doc. She listens and has a deep understanding of pain and what to do to reduce it. She cares about her patients and will never rush you or make you feel like your question is a bad one, no matter what it is. I would highly recommend her.
